WEBVTT

00:11.886 --> 00:13.263
That was Jenkins, though.

00:16.932 --> 00:19.394
He just didn't care
if he saw another sunrise.

00:22.771 --> 00:26.860
Okay. Let's shift back over to you.
You... You joined the force...

00:26.942 --> 00:29.027
'05. Started in the Northwest.

00:29.570 --> 00:33.324
And you told us that
you were doing small robberies,

00:33.407 --> 00:35.285
places like Belvedere Towers back then.

00:36.869 --> 00:38.704
That was around '08.

00:39.205 --> 00:42.333
And, just laying into some people,
like I said. Not any big stuff.

00:42.833 --> 00:44.501
If I may, you...

00:45.627 --> 00:48.506
sustained a gunshot wound in 2006.
What was that about?

00:50.258 --> 00:54.970
I caught a hot one when some dude
tried to rob me and he got shot.

00:59.516 --> 01:02.227
It's in the reports. You said that...
I'm sure you got all that.

01:02.311 --> 01:05.231
Actually, we have conflicting info
on that incident.

01:05.731 --> 01:06.941
Conflicting?

01:07.274 --> 01:11.863
One source indicated that
that shooting was actually drug related.

01:12.739 --> 01:16.159
A retaliation for some trafficking
you were involved with.

01:17.952 --> 01:20.746
Who told you that, Rayam?

01:22.499 --> 01:23.458
Shoot. It's...

01:24.791 --> 01:26.544
Jemell just trying to shine
the teacher's apple

01:26.627 --> 01:28.379
if he's laying stuff like that off on me.

01:28.463 --> 01:30.672
I mean, that ain't even credible.
What is... what is that?

01:32.299 --> 01:34.552
I mean, he's my boy,
but he always had his own problems.

01:34.886 --> 01:37.221
-What kind of problems?
-He likes women, for one.

01:38.347 --> 01:40.892
I'm just saying,
this man sets his watch to pussy.

01:44.645 --> 01:45.730
Excuse me, Miss Jensen.

01:52.237 --> 01:55.573
This shit goes way back
to when he was in uniform.

02:11.506 --> 02:14.132
He was lined up
with the underworld from the beginning.

02:15.343 --> 02:16.927
Jemell was married but, you know,

02:17.011 --> 02:19.055
-he had this girlfriend, Crystal Ferguson.
-What's up?

02:20.431 --> 02:22.432
You want... You want me to...
All right. See ya.

02:28.855 --> 02:31.317
She knew all the players west of M.L.K.

02:31.400 --> 02:33.570
When they'd be at their cribs,
when they wouldn't.

02:35.404 --> 02:37.197
She'd tell Jemell when they could be got.

02:41.578 --> 02:44.122
Fucking G-Money said that shit?

02:45.290 --> 02:49.460
Oh, wow. That's fucking funny.
He... he's acting like he's all pure now.

02:49.543 --> 02:50.670
Okay.

02:50.752 --> 02:52.922
-This fucking guy.
-Did Crystal Ferguson

02:53.005 --> 02:54.674
provide you with robbery targets?

03:00.137 --> 03:03.057
She mighta. I don't recall, exactly.

03:03.140 --> 03:04.684
This was when you and Detective Gondo

03:04.766 --> 03:06.685
were on the Violent Crime Impact Division
together?

03:07.520 --> 03:11.191
No. We went there later on.
And we weren't on VCID together.

03:12.065 --> 03:14.151
But we were doing our thing, for sure.

03:14.860 --> 03:15.944
But separate.

03:16.361 --> 03:19.532
In 2009, you fatally shot a citizen,
Shawn Cannady,

03:19.615 --> 03:21.075
in an alley off Pimlico Road.

03:24.536 --> 03:25.496
Self-defense.

03:26.247 --> 03:29.417
Uh-uh. No, no, not just the one.

03:30.500 --> 03:33.170
No, Jemell shot three people that year.

03:34.421 --> 03:35.422
Three.

03:35.840 --> 03:37.884
Get out of the car.
Get out of the car, now!

03:41.094 --> 03:43.472
Now, Rayam told me he did the thing.
I mean...

03:45.058 --> 03:46.141
he never denied it.

03:47.393 --> 03:51.104
Made it like the driver of a Lexus
was using his vehicle as a weapon,

03:51.773 --> 03:54.191
claimed the Lex had clipped Giordano.

03:54.734 --> 03:56.194
Jemell got off on that one.

03:58.403 --> 04:02.366
Palmere was right there on the scene,
coaching my man.

04:03.575 --> 04:06.329
Palmere, the deputy commissioner?

04:06.663 --> 04:09.665
Yeah. Colonel back then, but yeah.

04:17.674 --> 04:19.926
EMERGENCY MEDICAL SERVICES

04:20.009 --> 04:21.386
BALTIMORE CITY
FIRE DEPARTMENT

04:21.468 --> 04:22.595
Colonel.

04:23.012 --> 04:24.262
POLICE

04:38.194 --> 04:40.738
You felt that your life was in danger.
Got it?

04:51.915 --> 04:53.875
The Cannady shooting was justified.

04:56.420 --> 04:58.630
And you were subsequently suspended
for two years.

04:58.715 --> 05:01.758
Yeah, while they investigated
the thug from the Gary Brown stop.

05:03.094 --> 05:05.470
You lied to IAD investigators
regarding that one.

05:06.847 --> 05:09.641
-Right.
-Suspended with pay.

05:11.227 --> 05:13.353
I guess, you could say I was in limbo.
Yeah.

05:15.355 --> 05:19.819
And when you came off suspension
in 2012...

05:20.695 --> 05:23.948
Yeah. I went to the Gun Trace Task Force.

05:28.535 --> 05:30.788
What am I paying you
500 dollars an hour for?

05:41.132 --> 05:43.301
TRAYVON MARTIN - FREDDIE GRAY - MIKE BROWN

05:48.389 --> 05:50.391
I AM HERE BECAUSE ITS HOME

05:50.475 --> 05:52.392
POLICE

05:52.477 --> 05:53.519
BALTIMORE
POLICE

05:53.603 --> 05:54.687
2.7 KILO'S, $100,000.00

06:02.862 --> 06:03.821
-Back up.
-Back up.

06:05.531 --> 06:06.949
DOUBLE D BAIL BONDS
EVERYONE LOVES DOUBLE D'S

06:07.033 --> 06:11.536
Baltimore is a poster child
for the basic failure to stop lawlessness.

06:12.413 --> 06:14.332
No justice, no peace!

06:14.664 --> 06:16.875
I've heard your calls
for no justice, no peace.

06:16.958 --> 06:18.628
No justice, no peace!

06:27.636 --> 06:28.596
MAGIC

